Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86080,87890}Will the bus return here after two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.97,0:01:30.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87970,90790}The time has passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:34.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:91080,94150}If you walk in this way you\Nwill find a village nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:35.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:94180,95700}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95860,97470}I know that very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97500,98180}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:49.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106370,109670}I think I missed you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110450,111720}Here is my hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.28,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:111720,116280}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,300)}I Want To See My Grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119510,122110}Stop making this funny sound!\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:06.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:122380,126970}But I apologize for leaving\Nand forgetting our past days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:07.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127020,127710}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:09.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128130,129570}{\i1}Leave immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:11.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130010,131850}I don't want to see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142660,143410}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143460,144850}Grandma Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:27.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145260,147520}What's the matter, Jon Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147890,150290}Have you been throughout the day\Nwhen the teacher Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:31.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150320,151580}Y-yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:35.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151900,155260}{\i1}It's your fault because you read\Nthe book until late at night!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155550,158150}That is why you overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158980,161910}Grandma Forrest knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:46.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162060,166080}She looks from that window all the time so\Nshe knows all the news of the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166280,168280}John, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168430,169420}Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169720,171830}I just saw something very strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171850,172320}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172380,173130}Very strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:54.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173350,174010}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174220,176910}Grandma Forest act like I have\Nnever seen her before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:59.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177320,179460}She seemed to be arguing with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:00.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179640,180510}She argued?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180510,182450}You mean Grandma Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183660,185930}She poured water on him\Nfrom the second floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:09.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185950,189120}{\i1}It was a warm welcome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:10.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189220,190670}Well, it's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190820,193130}Because you left the village 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193490,196670}It's your fault because you\Nnever communicated with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:18.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196780,198520}Yes, thank you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198560,199190}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200700,202060}Twenty years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202240,204890}For me it was short...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:28.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205250,208610}In the meantime, I never thought of returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208810,209720}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209980,213860}In any case, I can't forgive such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213970,215200}Are you going back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:38.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215220,218020}I have to go back for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:42.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218750,222830}Over time she will actually listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223310,226540}Until my mother forgives me\NI will go to rest in the monastery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226830,227500}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227530,228160}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:50.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229490,230480}"Mom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:52.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232010,232880}{\i1}Uncle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:56.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233160,236700}I saw this guy in front of\NGrandma Forest's house, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236880,237610}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237880,239700}He's Grandma Forest's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239780,240540}- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:01.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240630,241930}Grandma Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241970,242980}Her son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:03.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243050,243670}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243760,247740}But Grandma Forest said:\N"I don't want to see your face!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:11.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247910,251550}Albert left the house after\Narguing with his parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251680,253670}That's why he left this village
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:15.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253910,255050}He argued with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287660,289190}He doesn't seem to work today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:53.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289470,293320}I wonder why Grandma Forest doesn't let him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293320,294650}Even though he is her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:55.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294780,295820}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295980,297780}Something might have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298100,300570}The son of Mrs. Forest left
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:05.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300770,305150}before your father came to this village so\Nwe can't anticipate the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305340,307750}But whatever the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:11.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307780,311120}he still wants to see Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.15,0:05:11.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311150,311790}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:12.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311820,312770}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312860,314200}Well, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314300,316120}Isn't this what a family does?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316270,317920}Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:22.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318060,322700}John, it certainly does, but there are\Nmany circumstances in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322810,325890}But, is definitely a parent\NI would like to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326020,327750}Dad, isn't that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:28.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327890,328430}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328990,329790}Hm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330080,331140}This is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:33.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332460,333690}Oh my God, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334000,336680}Oh... Where are you going on your holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336880,337480}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:41.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337570,341530}I'll have a short talk with Mrs. Forrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348510,351250}{\i1}What do you mean by living together?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352260,353520}So cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:56.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354070,356050}{\i1}Mrs. Forrest, just a moment!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357240,359780}What? Sam Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359810,360980}You came for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:02.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361010,362090}Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362250,366420}Weren't you watching the latest thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.61,0:06:10.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367610,370250}Can I come in for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375320,376210}{\i1}What is this...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376670,378990}So you can open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:23.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379150,383350}{\i1}Enter quickly and close the door\Nso no stranger enters here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385190,386860}{\i1}Regardless of that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387780,391430}Isn't that strange man your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391450,392570}My son, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392670,393340}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:34.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393470,394880}Sam Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394910,395520}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395560,398010}I don't have any son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398880,402580}My only family is my late husband George!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402600,404690}No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:45.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405130,405850}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407340,410150}I told you that I don't have any sons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412630,414220}No way, Mrs. Forrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414970,416700}F-father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:57.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416910,417590}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417620,419700}Dr. Hopper, call him quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419720,420880}Y--yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:10.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427750,430890}Well... It has little blood pressure only!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431070,434870}It's best to be not very active.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437320,438470}{\i1}I'm back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:20.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439060,440210}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:20.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440320,440940}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440960,443060}Will my grandmother come to our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:23.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443110,443700}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:27.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443770,447630}No... it seems she doesn't want to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:30.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448200,450960}She was very stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450990,452130}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:38.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452490,458260}In this picture looks like a very nice grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:42.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459440,462460}So, I will leave your present here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462880,464660}{\i1}John Carraclough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:48.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464970,468010}There's no need to treat me as a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468170,471470}Aren't you late for the kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471680,472220}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472370,474680}Do I have to do it, grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:57.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474840,477670}Are you still standing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:58.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477770,478980}And now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479080,480130}Yes, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483240,485960}Won't you go with him, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:14.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488890,494130}I always look at this part of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494220,495040}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495290,497460}Duhan is here much as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:22.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498080,502970}He thinks something good has happened to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503940,506530}This is Sam Carraclough's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506560,509970}I still remember the first day\Nwe met in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510000,512810}He was still young and went to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512950,517250}And the day when John got you,\Nyou were a puppy, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521830,522690}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:43.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523080,523930}And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:47.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523960,527330}This is an old picture of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.68,0:08:48.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527680,528970}{\i1}This is me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529070,532630}That's my late husband George,\Nand this kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533970,536630}It was a beautiful day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538250,540360}I wonder how things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:03.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540380,543850}got even bigger until they became like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:08.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544050,548740}In the end he left the house\Nand lived freely elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549530,553100}George was working hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:17.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553120,557940}to make money for my son Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:22.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558140,562110}But that boy stole the golden piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562600,563340}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563970,566440}Then I didn't know how he lives\Nand where he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:30.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566650,570080}Even when his father died, he never came!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:34.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570440,574080}And when he understood his sin\Nhe came after he left this village
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574100,576420}to ask me to live with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:39.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578020,579460}Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580030,581420}{\i1}You bastard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587500,588440}{\i1}Whoa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588640,589860}It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591490,593430}You are late, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593530,596020}Have you been to Grandma Forest all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596910,598960}And Grandma Forrest's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599070,602360}Eh? Lassie, did you know\Nthat about grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607960,609410}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609440,612120}Ah, someone is sitting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612150,613420}{\i1}I wonder who is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:17.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617030,617900}{\i1}Sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:18.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617920,618510}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:19.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618820,619880}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619910,621130}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621160,623160}Hurt? You are wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623270,627460}I just lost something very precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627880,629080}Very precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:32.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629350,632480}Yes, it's a necklace I got from my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632610,633930}A necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634270,637440}It's very precious for my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641030,642400}Ah, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642770,644820}I'm happy, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:47.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644890,647380}Tell me, we have met you\Nbut we haven't asked who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647580,648800}Yes, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649220,651350}I'm Roy George Forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651460,652460}Forrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652610,655200}Oh, could he be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655340,657270}Grandma Forrest's grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657350,658160}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663740,665970}Do you know my grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666250,668230}We really know her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:08.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668350,668940}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:14.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668970,674100}We know her, yet we didn't know\Nanything about grandmother's grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:18.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674100,678650}I didn't know, it was a novelty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:19.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678670,679330}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679410,680660}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680880,682740}I also didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682770,684720}about having a grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684750,685430}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685550,686530}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686560,689340}If you don't know anything\Nabout your grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689370,692400}it means that you are\Nvery terrible and stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692440,693100}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:35.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693350,695370}Stop it! This is rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:37.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695390,697580}Ah... right... sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:39.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698610,699860}That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:43.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699860,703290}My father is the one who\Noppressed my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703610,706650}That's why I wanted to see my grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706680,708800}but that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709320,712790}I have an old picture of my grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712900,715750}She looks very nice and she smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:56.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715770,716390}- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717010,718820}I looked at the picture a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718930,721450}That's why I wanted to see my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721930,722980}{\i1}Also...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:04.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723080,724060}Also?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724950,728960}I haven't told my father and mother\Nabout coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729080,730270}...alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733060,734600}So let's go, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734630,736740}I'll tell you about your grandmother's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736790,737360}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:25.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745270,745830}{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:26.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745860,746540}- Oh!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746640,749300}{\i1}My son and his mother want to see you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749570,751060}He's your grandson, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751910,754800}Mom, you want to see him, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754920,756400}{\i1}My grandson?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756480,760610}{\i1}My only family is my late husband George!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:42.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760630,762450}{\i1}I don't have any children!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762550,765620}{\i1}I don't have any child, I mean\NI don't have any grandson!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:48.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765740,768880}{\i1}How should I meet strangers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:49.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768880,769670}{\i1}But Mom...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:50.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769940,770900}{\i1}Leave!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771040,773930}{\i1}If you don't leave, I will pour water on you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:54.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774020,774730}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780590,783440}Grandmother... don't want to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783510,784970}It's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785090,786010}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786030,786630}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787140,790050}She wants to see you, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790220,792120}But she's a little stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:14.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792230,794810}I think she doesn't want to say\Nthat she really wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:15.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795120,795810}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796360,798510}Can't we do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798690,799600}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799700,800960}{\i1}Listen John...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:21.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801110,801670}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:23.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801750,803150}This is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803500,806800}I can't believe my mother is so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806800,809580}What? Do you want to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:30.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809670,810880}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811060,813000}Since I left this village
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:37.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813020,817330}I went to many places and\Nstarted building my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817870,820780}In the end I stayed in a house of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820900,822890}And so I can welcome her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823070,825010}That's what I was thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825450,828020}It took me 20 years to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828040,829090}She's 20 years older!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829450,830710}Ah-ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:54.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830900,834780}I can't give up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:14:00.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834880,840940}You can't do that easily after\Nyou decided to leave the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840940,841870}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841990,844980}I don't know if I inherited this\Nfrom my mother or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845280,846730}{\i1}My grandson?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:07.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847230,847950}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848500,849340}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849810,852520}What brings you to my home, John Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852570,853250}E-e-eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:18.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854780,858520}I brought some cookies with me,\NI want to have tea with you, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858780,860910}I wonder what wind carry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861020,863200}Well okay, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:30.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865420,870270}Today I haven't come alone,\Nis it okay if my cousin comes with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:31.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870630,871400}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871750,872900}This face...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873330,876180}{\i1}Albert! It's not possible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879570,881130}Now, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881310,883550}I don't want to meet her as her grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883700,886090}If I tell her that I'm her grandson,\Nshe'll throw me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886090,887420}I'm sure you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889730,892580}Well, is it okay to have tea here sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:53.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893070,893770}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:55.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894910,895930}{\i1}My grandmother...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896910,899140}Your cousin, John Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:02.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899760,902470}The person that's with you doesn't seem to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902500,903350}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:06.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903380,906030}Today he came to visit me in my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:06.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906060,906690}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906710,909900}I didn't know that you have a cousin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909900,911860}Really? But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:13.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912050,913320}{\i1}John...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913670,914730}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914750,917000}Aren't you here? You're away?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917100,919460}They're calling you, John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919490,921200}Now answer them immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:23.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:921320,923300}Yes, I'll go at them for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923320,925950}Roy, pour tea for grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926160,927240}Oh... oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927390,928620}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928770,931070}I can't, Sandy calls me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:31.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931150,931900}See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936170,937880}You can go with him quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:40.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938000,940050}No, I will give you tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944090,945010}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:50.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948610,950540}Why do you stand like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951130,954600}If you want to drink tea,\Nyou should bring a chair and sit on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:55.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954660,955860}Ah... okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963880,965020}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965690,967620}My name is Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968780,969760}Roy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:15.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971320,975460}Hm! Your parents souldn't\Ngive you that funny name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978410,979290}Does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:21.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979560,981750}{\i1}Does this village produce coal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981900,982660}{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983000,986550}My grandfather was a worker in the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986800,987920}Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988300,989640}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989790,991600}My husband too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:34.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992350,994040}He was working in that mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994120,995490}What a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995550,998270}A man was proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998420,999550}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000100,1002480}And... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:43.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002510,1003180}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:48.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003910,1008940}I also think that your father\Nis proud of your hard work
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.16,0:16:52.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009160,1012770}because he was a mine worker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:54.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013980,1014820}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014820,1016470}Oh, I was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:57.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016580,1017590}That's unfortunate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:04.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023230,1024240}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024410,1025140}Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:08.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025260,1028400}Before my birth my father became a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028420,1030730}That's why he visited many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030960,1033980}He was always yearning\Nfor such a life of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033980,1035960}I am shocked by his situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:16.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035990,1036730}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:20.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037000,1040020}I don't want to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:28.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046360,1048200}She's not looking here, it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058360,1060090}I can't hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:43.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060270,1063030}They don't seem to speak at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:43.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063090,1063810}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064010,1066910}Listen, Colin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067040,1068280}Yes, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069610,1071650}Now, isn't the time to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071730,1073490}John's cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073600,1074340}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077640,1079620}That's it, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:00.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079910,1080780}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086050,1088480}Ah! Don't do such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089810,1091940}Lassie, let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093410,1094200}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095260,1096400}{\i1}T-t-this is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097190,1098850}{\i1}Give it to me, Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100690,1102040}T-this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:24.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102190,1104400}I got it from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:25.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104620,1105640}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:28.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105770,1108400}This golden piece dates back\Nto the fifteenth century!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108620,1110330}Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112920,1116370}This is the gold piece that George took!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116400,1119660}How could a child like you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119690,1122050}I didn't know anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122790,1125560}This is because my father\Ndidn't tell me any word!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126260,1128720}However, regardless of the extent of poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128900,1132260}it can't be replaced by money\Nbecause it was as precious as he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132370,1133160}Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:55.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133870,1135100}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135250,1137800}{\i1}When my father became a sailor,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:02.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137940,1142430}{\i1}he was afflicted with serious illness and yet\Nhe worked hard to earn money for us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:03.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142560,1143400}...But
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:07.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143560,1147740}But he never thought\Nof replacing this gold with money,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:09.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147770,1149190}but rather did his best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150300,1151420}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152330,1155140}So he didn't sold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:20.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157350,1160950}That is why he worked hard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:23.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160980,1163460}not to forget those days!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163680,1164600}Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164620,1165300}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:28.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165480,1168550}Don't stay there and come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169730,1172190}{\i1}Because of my age I can't hear you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172310,1174410}{\i1}Come closer and talk to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174750,1175580}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175990,1178780}I'm very happy because I came to this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:42.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179060,1182020}My father didn't work in the mine,\Nand became a sailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182130,1184140}yet I am still proud of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:47.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184340,1187960}The ship he was working in was operated by coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:52.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188030,1192430}The furnace of the ship was reddening, and it\Nwas the coal that led him to the seven seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:56.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192680,1196150}Charcoal xxx my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198300,1200570}I'm glad I came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200780,1202940}And found my grandfather here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205360,1207110}Grandmother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207310,1208700}I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208800,1211820}Roy, you are... my grandson...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:12.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211820,1212960}Grandmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216170,1218410}{\i1}Are you here, John Carraclough?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218520,1220030}{\i1}- Show yourself immediately!{\i0}\N- Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220810,1222450}You knew that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.67,0:20:24.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222670,1224820}Continue from Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224950,1227410}But my father returned to the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:30.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227440,1230140}But he is still in Jones' shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:33.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230200,1233490}He won't go today as long as he thinks about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:38.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233840,1238090}He thinks about what he will do all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238090,1239370}{\i1}No, you're wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239400,1240790}Grandmother, I hid him from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241260,1243260}Mr. Albert is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243260,1245530}He's been here a while\Nand he' s listening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:46.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245550,1246210}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:47.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246530,1247270}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247850,1251830}That's why you tried to dismiss\Nmy theory, John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252550,1253520}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:57.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253670,1257000}I will live in this village and\NI won't leave again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:57.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257000,1257930}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258130,1260880}I won't go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263240,1265570}Welcome back, Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265970,1267030}Mom!
